narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would definitely recommend German to a fellow student, because not only was it fun learning a new language, but it also helped me gain insight on the similarities of the different languages, and how English is Germanic language! It was quite interesting!

If you want to learn German, of course you should take this class. However, be aware about pronounciation and keep track of the readings, because it's what's going to make you really take advantage of the course.
It was a fun class that was very informative and educational. Not too much work.
